g.ns0:text: \\begin{align*}\nf_{Y}(y)dy &= \\dfrac{1}{\\beta^{\\alpha}}\\frac{1}{\\Gamma(\\alpha)}(\\beta y)^{\\alpha-1}e^{-\\frac{\\beta y}{\\beta}}d(\\beta y)\\\\\n &= \\frac{1}{\\cancel{\\beta^{\\alpha}}}\\frac{1}{\\Gamma(\\alpha)}\\cancel{\\beta^{\\alpha-1}} y^{\\alpha-1}e^{-y}\\cancel{\\beta} dy\\\\\n &= \\underbrace{\\frac{1}{\\Gamma(\\alpha)} y^{\\alpha-1}e^{-t}}_{\\text{standard gamma}}dy\n\\end{align*}
